Date: Fri, 11 Jan 2013 17:58:50 +0530
Subject: MMC : Adding 'number of MMC slots' information to DTS files

Removing board specific hardcode for 'number of MMC slots'
and moving 'number of MMC slots' information to DTS files.
[Based on SDK 3.2]
Signed-off-by: Quanyang Wang <quanyang.wang@windriver.com>
Signed-off-by: Nam Ninh <nam.ninh@windriver.com>

diff --git a/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux.dts b/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux.dts
index c75dc8e..3747612 100644
--- a/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux.dts
+++ b/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux.dts
@@ -43,6 +43,9 @@
 				owner = <1>;
 				sharedcfg = <0x1f000000>;
 			};
+                        mmc {
+                                slots = <2>;
+                        };
 			memory {
 				reg = <0x01000000 0x0B000000	// 176M at 16M
 					0x20000000 0xa0000000>;  // 2586M at 512M
